Line3.789BF: Hm. Not at first. But then he almost killed me. Marked my skin, put a demon in my head. I will take pleasure from his death.
Line5.789BF: The hunt will soon be over. You’ve angered him. He will come to you. And I will be there when that happens. If fate allows, let it be my hand that ends him.
MenuLabel: “Your hunt for Elias, is it personal?”
